    A["[]"] --> B["head(_)"]
    B --> C["undefined"]\`}
  mobile={\`flowchart TB
    A["[]"] --> B["head(_)"]
    B --> C["undefined"]\`}
/>

### Native Equivalent

\`\`\`typescript
// ❌ head(arr)
// ✅ arr[0]
// ✅ arr.at(0)
\`\`\`

---

## Use Cases

### Get first element 📌

Get the first element of an array.

<div style={{display: 'flex', flexWrap: 'wrap', gap: '8px', marginTop: '8px', marginBottom: '16px'}}>
